WEBVTT

00:00:00.697 --> 00:00:03.449
Take a bit of toast, mate. Go on.

00:00:03.659 --> 00:00:06.861
Ron's right.
You'll need your strength today.

00:00:07.079 --> 00:00:09.285
I'm not hungry.

00:00:09.873 --> 00:00:15.496
Good luck today, Potter.
You've proven yourself against a troll.

00:00:15.712 --> 00:00:18.879
A game of Quidditch
should be easy work.

00:00:19.091 --> 00:00:22.211
Even if it is against Slytherin.

